1. clone the repo from github
  git clone https://github.com/urbanairship/tessera.git


2. cd tessera

3. virtualenv .

4. . bin/activate

5. cd tessera-server

6. pip install -r requirements.txt
   pip install -r dev-requirements.txt
   
7. cd ..
   cd tessera-frontend

9. make sure npm and nodejs-* are installed already and then run the following commands
   grunt is a javascript task runner 
     npm install -g grunt-cli
     npm install
     grunt
   grunt should be up and running 
   
10. grunt watch &
    to run grunt in the background 
  
